data.description: REDUCED!! Beautiful 3/2.5/1 car garage townhouse in sought after, GATED, Bay Shore Commons, close to I75, stores, restaurants,& excellent health care facilities. Only THREE YEARS NEW, Low HOA. This home boasts of high-end upgrades including engineered wood plank flooring, double paver driveway for 2 cars, downstairs powder room, Maytag washer & dryer in upstairs laundry, top of the line Refrigerator as well as closet organizers throughout. You needn't worry about the stairs since owners installed a CHAIRLIFT. This home provides easy access for wheelchair or scooter needs. Principle suite has walk in shower and walk in closet. ELECTRIC STORM SHUTTERS upstairs & ACCORDIAN SHUTTERS on first floor. Just steps to community swimming pool and guest parking.
